node.text: The best advice I've heard is to not let your desire for perfection lead to procrastination, if you want to start something just start it. Unless you’re like me, who puts the “pro” in procrastinate 🤠

node.title: Another day, another deadline induced panic 😅 Leave an 🥚 if you relate 👇
